    - name: '23: '
      title: 
      number: 23
      content: 'So may God shower his peace upon you, my beloved friends. And may
        the blessings of faith and love fill your hearts from God the Father and
        from our Lord Jesus, the Messiah. '
      comments: []
    - name: '24: '
      title: 
      number: 24
      content: Abundant grace will be with you all as each of you love our Lord Jesus
        Christ without corruption. Amen!Love in Christ,Paul
      comments: []
